SELECT `a`.`Id`, `a`.`Description`, `a`.`ObtainableScore`, `a`.`FileUrl`, `s`.`SubjectName`, `a`.`TeacherId`, `c`.`ClassName`, `c0`.`GradeName`, `a`.`SchoolId`, `a`.`CampusId`, `s0`.`SessionName`, `t`.`TermName`, `a`.`IsActive`, `a`.`DueDate`, `a`.`DateUploaded`, `a`.`LastDateUpdated`
FROM `Assignments` AS `a`
INNER JOIN `SchoolSubjects` AS `s` ON `a`.`SubjectId` = `s`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Classes` AS `c` ON `a`.`ClassId` = `c`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ClassGrades` AS `c0` ON `a`.`ClassGradeId` = `c0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Sessions` AS `s0` ON `a`.`SessionId` = `s0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Terms` AS `t` ON `a`.`TermId` = `t`.`Id`
WHERE `a`.`Id` = @__ass_Id_0

2021-07-18 17:12:30.104 +01:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__examScr_Id_0='?' (DbType = Int64)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT `e`.`Id`, `e`.`SchoolId`, `e`.`CampusId`, `c`.`ClassName`, `c0`.`GradeName`, `s`.`SessionName`, `t`.`TermName`, `s0`.`SubjectName`, `s1`.`DepartmentName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s2`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s2`.`LastName`) AS `StudentName`, `s2`.`AdmissionNumber`, `e`.`MarkObtainable`, `e`.`MarkObtained`, `s3`.`CategoryName`, `s4`.`SubCategoryName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s5`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s5`.`LastName`) AS `TeachersName`, `e`.`DateUploaded`, `e`.`DateUpdated`
FROM `ExaminationScores` AS `e`
INNER JOIN `Classes` AS `c` ON `e`.`ClassId` = `c`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ClassGrades` AS `c0` ON `e`.`ClassGradeId` = `c0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Sessions` AS `s` ON `e`.`SessionId` = `s`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Terms` AS `t` ON `e`.`TermId` = `t`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolSubjects` AS `s0` ON `e`.`SubjectId` = `s0`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN `SubjectDepartment` AS `s1` ON `e`.`DepartmentId` = `s1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Students` AS `s2` ON `e`.`StudentId` = `s2`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreCategory` AS `s3` ON `e`.`CategoryId` = `s3`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreSubCategoryConfig` AS `s4` ON `e`.`SubCategoryId` = `s4`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolUsers` AS `s5` ON `e`.`TeacherId` = `s5`.`Id`
WHERE `e`.`Id` = @__examScr_Id_0

SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`SchoolId`, `c`.`CampusId`, `c0`.`ClassName`, `c1`.`GradeName`, `s`.`SessionName`, `t`.`TermName`, `s0`.`SubjectName`, `s1`.`DepartmentName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s2`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s2`.`LastName`) AS `StudentName`, `s2`.`AdmissionNumber`, `c`.`MarkObtainable`, `c`.`MarkObtained`, `s3`.`CategoryName`, `s4`.`SubCategoryName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s5`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s5`.`LastName`) AS `TeachersName`, `c`.`DateUploaded`, `c`.`DateUpdated`
FROM `ContinousAssessmentScores` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `Classes` AS `c0` ON `c`.`ClassId` = `c0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ClassGrades` AS `c1` ON `c`.`ClassGradeId` = `c1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Sessions` AS `s` ON `c`.`SessionId` = `s`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Terms` AS `t` ON `c`.`TermId` = `t`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolSubjects` AS `s0` ON `c`.`SubjectId` = `s0`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN `SubjectDepartment` AS `s1` ON `c`.`DepartmentId` = `s1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Students` AS `s2` ON `c`.`StudentId` = `s2`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreCategory` AS `s3` ON `c`.`CategoryId` = `s3`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreSubCategoryConfig` AS `s4` ON `c`.`SubCategoryId` = `s4`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolUsers` AS `s5` ON `c`.`TeacherId` = `s5`.`Id`
WHERE `c`.`Id` = @__caScore_Id_0

FROM `ContinousAssessmentScores` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `Classes` AS `c0` ON `c`.`ClassId` = `c0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ClassGrades` AS `c1` ON `c`.`ClassGradeId` = `c1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Sessions` AS `s` ON `c`.`SessionId` = `s`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Terms` AS `t` ON `c`.`TermId` = `t`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolSubjects` AS `s0` ON `c`.`SubjectId` = `s0`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN `SubjectDepartment` AS `s1` ON `c`.`DepartmentId` = `s1`.`Id`

INNER JOIN `ScoreSubCategoryConfig` AS `s4` ON `c`.`SubCategoryId` = `s4`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolUsers` AS `s5` ON `c`.`TeacherId` = `s5`.`Id`
WHERE `c`.`Id` = @__caScore_Id_0

SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`SchoolId`, `c`.`CampusId`, `c0`.`ClassName`, `c1`.`GradeName`, `s`.`SessionName`, `t`.`TermName`, `s0`.`SubjectName`, `s1`.`DepartmentName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s2`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s2`.`LastName`) AS `StudentName`, `s2`.`AdmissionNumber`, `c`.`MarkObtainable`, `c`.`MarkObtained`, `s3`.`CategoryName`, `s4`.`SubCategoryName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s5`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s5`.`LastName`) AS `TeachersName`, `c`.`DateUploaded`, `c`.`DateUpdated`
FROM `ContinousAssessmentScores` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `Classes` AS `c0` ON `c`.`ClassId` = `c0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ClassGrades` AS `c1` ON `c`.`ClassGradeId` = `c1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Sessions` AS `s` ON `c`.`SessionId` = `s`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Terms` AS `t` ON `c`.`TermId` = `t`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolSubjects` AS `s0` ON `c`.`SubjectId` = `s0`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN `SubjectDepartment` AS `s1` ON `c`.`DepartmentId` = `s1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Students` AS `s2` ON `c`.`StudentId` = `s2`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreCategory` AS `s3` ON `c`.`CategoryId` = `s3`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreSubCategoryConfig` AS `s4` ON `c`.`SubCategoryId` = `s4`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolUsers` AS `s5` ON `c`.`TeacherId` = `s5`.`Id`
WHERE `c`.`Id` = @__caScore_Id_0

SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`SchoolId`, `c`.`CampusId`, `c0`.`ClassName`, `c1`.`GradeName`, `s`.`SessionName`, `t`.`TermName`, `s0`.`SubjectName`, `s1`.`DepartmentName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s2`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s2`.`LastName`) AS `StudentName`, `s2`.`AdmissionNumber`, `c`.`MarkObtainable`, `c`.`MarkObtained`, `s3`.`CategoryName`, `s4`.`SubCategoryName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s5`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s5`.`LastName`) AS `TeachersName`, `c`.`DateUploaded`, `c`.`DateUpdated`
FROM `ContinousAssessmentScores` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `Classes` AS `c0` ON `c`.`ClassId` = `c0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ClassGrades` AS `c1` ON `c`.`ClassGradeId` = `c1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Sessions` AS `s` ON `c`.`SessionId` = `s`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Terms` AS `t` ON `c`.`TermId` = `t`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolSubjects` AS `s0` ON `c`.`SubjectId` = `s0`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN `SubjectDepartment` AS `s1` ON `c`.`DepartmentId` = `s1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Students` AS `s2` ON `c`.`StudentId` = `s2`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreCategory` AS `s3` ON `c`.`CategoryId` = `s3`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreSubCategoryConfig` AS `s4` ON `c`.`SubCategoryId` = `s4`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolUsers` AS `s5` ON `c`.`TeacherId` = `s5`.`Id`
WHERE `c`.`Id` = @__caScore_Id_0

SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`SchoolId`, `c`.`CampusId`, `c0`.`ClassName`, `c1`.`GradeName`, `s`.`SessionName`, `t`.`TermName`, `s0`.`SubjectName`, `s1`.`DepartmentName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s2`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s2`.`LastName`) AS `StudentName`, `s2`.`AdmissionNumber`, `c`.`MarkObtainable`, `c`.`MarkObtained`, `s3`.`CategoryName`, `s4`.`SubCategoryName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s5`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s5`.`LastName`) AS `TeachersName`, `c`.`DateUploaded`, `c`.`DateUpdated`
FROM `ContinousAssessmentScores` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `Classes` AS `c0` ON `c`.`ClassId` = `c0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ClassGrades` AS `c1` ON `c`.`ClassGradeId` = `c1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Sessions` AS `s` ON `c`.`SessionId` = `s`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Terms` AS `t` ON `c`.`TermId` = `t`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolSubjects` AS `s0` ON `c`.`SubjectId` = `s0`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN `SubjectDepartment` AS `s1` ON `c`.`DepartmentId` = `s1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Students` AS `s2` ON `c`.`StudentId` = `s2`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreCategory` AS `s3` ON `c`.`CategoryId` = `s3`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreSubCategoryConfig` AS `s4` ON `c`.`SubCategoryId` = `s4`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolUsers` AS `s5` ON `c`.`TeacherId` = `s5`.`Id`
WHERE `c`.`Id` = @__caScore_Id_0

INNER JOIN `Classes` AS `c` ON `r`.`ClassId` = `c`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ClassGrades` AS `c0` ON `r`.`ClassGradeId` = `c0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Terms` AS `t` ON `r`.`TermId` = `t`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Sessions` AS `s1` ON `r`.`SessionId` = `s1`.`Id`

2021-07-18 17:41:11.943 +01:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__8__locals1_obj_ClassGradeId_0='?' (DbType = Int64), @__8__locals1_obj_ClassId_1='?' (DbType = Int64), @__8__locals1_obj_SchoolId_2='?' (DbType = Int64), @__8__locals1_obj_CampusId_3='?' (DbType = Int64), @__8__locals1_obj_SessionId_4='?' SELECT `r`.`Id`, `r`.`SchoolId`, `r`.`CampusId`, `r`.`StudentId`, `s`.`FirstName`, `s`.`LastName`, `r`.`AdmissionNumber`, `r`.`CAScore`, `r`.`ExamScore`, `r`.`TotalScore`, `r`.`Position`, `r`.`SubjectId`, `s0`.`SubjectName`, `r`.`ClassId`, `c`.`ClassName`, `r`.`ClassGradeId`, `c0`.`GradeName`, `r`.`TermId`, `t`.`TermName`, `r`.`SessionId`, `s1`.`SessionName`, `r`.`AveragePosition`, `r`.`AverageScore`, `r`.`Grade`, `r`.`Remark`, `r`.`DepartmentId`, `s2`.`DepartmentName`, `r`.`AverageTotalScore`, `r`.`CumulativeCA_Score`, `r`.`FirstTermTotalScore`, `r`.`SecondTermTotalScore`, `r`.`DateComputed`
FROM `ReportCardData` AS `r`
INNER JOIN `Students` AS `s` ON `r`.`StudentId` = `s`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolSubjects` AS `s0` ON `r`.`SubjectId` = `s0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Classes` AS `c` ON `r`.`ClassId` = `c`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ClassGrades` AS `c0` ON `r`.`ClassGradeId` = `c0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Terms` AS `t` ON `r`.`TermId` = `t`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Sessions` AS `s1` ON `r`.`SessionId` = `s1`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN `SubjectDepartment` AS `s2` ON `r`.`DepartmentId` = `s2`.`Id`
WHERE (((((`r`.`ClassGradeId` = @__8__locals1_obj_ClassGradeId_0) AND (`r`.`ClassId` = @__8__locals1_obj_ClassId_1)) AND (`r`.`SchoolId` = @__8__locals1_obj_SchoolId_2)) AND (`r`.`CampusId` = @__8__locals1_obj_CampusId_3)) AND (`r`.`SessionId` = @__8__locals1_obj_SessionId_4)) AND (`r`.`TermId` = @__8__locals1_obj_TermId_5)
ORDER BY `r`.`TotalScore` DESC

SELECT `r`.`Id`, `r`.`SchoolId`, `r`.`CampusId`, `r`.`StudentId`, `s`.`FirstName`, `s`.`LastName`, `r`.`AdmissionNumber`, `r`.`TotalScore`, `r`.`TotalScoreObtainable`, `r`.`PercentageScore`, `r`.`Position`, `r`.`SubjectComputed`, `r`.`ClassId`, `c`.`ClassName`, `r`.`ClassGradeId`, `c0`.`GradeName`, `r`.`TermId`, `t`.`TermName`, `r`.`SessionId`, `s0`.`SessionName`, `r`.`DateComputed`
FROM `ReportCardPosition` AS `r`
INNER JOIN `Students` AS `s` ON `r`.`StudentId` = `s`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Classes` AS `c` ON `r`.`ClassId` = `c`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ClassGrades` AS `c0` ON `r`.`ClassGradeId` = `c0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Terms` AS `t` ON `r`.`TermId` = `t`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Sessions` AS `s0` ON `r`.`SessionId` = `s0`.`Id`
WHERE (((((`r`.`ClassGradeId` = @__8__locals1_obj_ClassGradeId_0) AND (`r`.`ClassId` = @__8__locals1_obj_ClassId_1)) AND (`r`.`SchoolId` = @__8__locals1_obj_SchoolId_2)) AND (`r`.`CampusId` = @__8__locals1_obj_CampusId_3)) AND (`r`.`SessionId` = @__8__locals1_obj_SessionId_4)) AND (`r`.`TermId` = @__8__locals1_obj_TermId_5)
ORDER BY `r`.`TotalScore` DESC

SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`SchoolId`, `c`.`CampusId`, `c0`.`ClassName`, `c1`.`GradeName`, `s`.`SessionName`, `t`.`TermName`, `s0`.`SubjectName`, `s1`.`DepartmentName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s2`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s2`.`LastName`) AS `StudentName`, `s2`.`AdmissionNumber`, `c`.`MarkObtainable`, `c`.`MarkObtained`, `s3`.`CategoryName`, `s4`.`SubCategoryName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s5`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s5`.`LastName`) AS `TeachersName`, `c`.`DateUploaded`, `c`.`DateUpdated`
FROM `ContinousAssessmentScores` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `Classes` AS `c0` ON `c`.`ClassId` = `c0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ClassGrades` AS `c1` ON `c`.`ClassGradeId` = `c1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Sessions` AS `s` ON `c`.`SessionId` = `s`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Terms` AS `t` ON `c`.`TermId` = `t`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolSubjects` AS `s0` ON `c`.`SubjectId` = `s0`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN `SubjectDepartment` AS `s1` ON `c`.`DepartmentId` = `s1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Students` AS `s2` ON `c`.`StudentId` = `s2`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreCategory` AS `s3` ON `c`.`CategoryId` = `s3`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreSubCategoryConfig` AS `s4` ON `c`.`SubCategoryId` = `s4`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolUsers` AS `s5` ON `c`.`TeacherId` = `s5`.`Id`
WHERE `c`.`Id` = @__caScore_Id_0

SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`SchoolId`, `c`.`CampusId`, `c0`.`ClassName`, `c1`.`GradeName`, `s`.`SessionName`, `t`.`TermName`, `s0`.`SubjectName`, `s1`.`DepartmentName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s2`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s2`.`LastName`) AS `StudentName`, `s2`.`AdmissionNumber`, `c`.`MarkObtainable`, `c`.`MarkObtained`, `s3`.`CategoryName`, `s4`.`SubCategoryName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s5`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s5`.`LastName`) AS `TeachersName`, `c`.`DateUploaded`, `c`.`DateUpdated`
FROM `ContinousAssessmentScores` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `Classes` AS `c0` ON `c`.`ClassId` = `c0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ClassGrades` AS `c1` ON `c`.`ClassGradeId` = `c1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Sessions` AS `s` ON `c`.`SessionId` = `s`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Terms` AS `t` ON `c`.`TermId` = `t`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolSubjects` AS `s0` ON `c`.`SubjectId` = `s0`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN `SubjectDepartment` AS `s1` ON `c`.`DepartmentId` = `s1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Students` AS `s2` ON `c`.`StudentId` = `s2`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreCategory` AS `s3` ON `c`.`CategoryId` = `s3`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreSubCategoryConfig` AS `s4` ON `c`.`SubCategoryId` = `s4`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolUsers` AS `s5` ON `c`.`TeacherId` = `s5`.`Id`
WHERE `c`.`Id` = @__caScore_Id_0

SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`SchoolId`, `c`.`CampusId`, `c0`.`ClassName`, `c1`.`GradeName`, `s`.`SessionName`, `t`.`TermName`, `s0`.`SubjectName`, `s1`.`DepartmentName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s2`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s2`.`LastName`) AS `StudentName`, `s2`.`AdmissionNumber`, `c`.`MarkObtainable`, `c`.`MarkObtained`, `s3`.`CategoryName`, `s4`.`SubCategoryName`, CONCAT(CONCAT(`s5`.`FirstName`, ' '), `s5`.`LastName`) AS `TeachersName`, `c`.`DateUploaded`, `c`.`DateUpdated`
FROM `ContinousAssessmentScores` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `Classes` AS `c0` ON `c`.`ClassId` = `c0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ClassGrades` AS `c1` ON `c`.`ClassGradeId` = `c1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Sessions` AS `s` ON `c`.`SessionId` = `s`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Terms` AS `t` ON `c`.`TermId` = `t`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolSubjects` AS `s0` ON `c`.`SubjectId` = `s0`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN `SubjectDepartment` AS `s1` ON `c`.`DepartmentId` = `s1`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Students` AS `s2` ON `c`.`StudentId` = `s2`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreCategory` AS `s3` ON `c`.`CategoryId` = `s3`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `ScoreSubCategoryConfig` AS `s4` ON `c`.`SubCategoryId` = `s4`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `SchoolUsers` AS `s5` ON `c`.`TeacherId` = `s5`.`Id`
WHERE `c`.`Id` = @__caScore_Id_0
